2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the impact of hardware impairments on the performance of multiple-antenna base stations, which is a topic relevant to networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper analyzes the distortion correlation in hardware impairments, which is a topic related to systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the impact of hardware impairments on the uplink spectral efficiency, which is a topic relevant to multimedia systems. 
5. cs.COM (Computers and Society) - Although less likely, the paper may also be relevant to the societal impact of hardware impairments on communication systems.
